    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PVE Story missions with up to 4 players! </strong>(Work In Progress)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the game story through missions, alone or with up to other 3 friends! <br>More difficulties are unlocked upon completion. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018340/extras/50e5839eba3e7c58df345bc831c92edb.poster.avif?t=1765010726\" width=600 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018340/extras/50e5839eba3e7c58df345bc831c92edb.webm?t=1765010726\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018340/extras/50e5839eba3e7c58df345bc831c92edb.mp4?t=1765010726\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PVP Gamemodes!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can invite your friend to a duel or have a duel against a random opponent, more PVP Gamemodes coming soon! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018340/extras/f271341f8b4e12d3ce8ace65ed5cdf6f.poster.avif?t=1765010726\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018340/extras/f271341f8b4e12d3ce8ace65ed5cdf6f.webm?t=1765010726\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018340/extras/f271341f8b4e12d3ce8ace65ed5cdf6f.mp4?t=1765010726\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Loadout System!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your loadout, if you don't like an ability, just change it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can equip 1 generic dash, 1 generic melee and 4 character specific abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dashes and melees are usable by all characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018340/extras/f095b1b0c89ddfb09f543a3b4f5a4875.poster.avif?t=1765010726\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018340/extras/f095b1b0c89ddfb09f543a3b4f5a4875.webm?t=1765010726\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018340/extras/f095b1b0c89ddfb09f543a3b4f5a4875.mp4?t=1765010726\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Many Abilities to unlock, soon more!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Currently, there are 16 abilities to equip and try out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The leveling system is a work in progress, so all abilities are unlocked by default, but on release you will be able to level up your account</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And unlock new characters, level up each character separately and unlock new abilities with that specific character. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Here are some of the abilities:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018340/extras/55a4d81be661fd7d80bdec07400e8abc.poster.avif?t=1765010726\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018340/extras/55a4d81be661fd7d80bdec07400e8abc.webm?t=1765010726\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018340/extras/55a4d81be661fd7d80bdec07400e8abc.mp4?t=1765010726\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018340/extras/7a2a88b78ece426c02e144909b2cdcb3.poster.avif?t=1765010726\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018340/extras/7a2a88b78ece426c02e144909b2cdcb3.webm?t=1765010726\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018340/extras/7a2a88b78ece426c02e144909b2cdcb3.mp4?t=1765010726\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018340/extras/90cfa1fe05656afeb9f6cf8f5b25d748.poster.avif?t=1765010726\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018340/extras/90cfa1fe05656afeb9f6cf8f5b25d748.webm?t=1765010726\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018340/extras/90cfa1fe05656afeb9f6cf8f5b25d748.mp4?t=1765010726\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018340/extras/beadb989fc8a2135641b3bb9adee64b9.poster.avif?t=1765010726\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018340/extras/beadb989fc8a2135641b3bb9adee64b9.webm?t=1765010726\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018340/extras/beadb989fc8a2135641b3bb9adee64b9.mp4?t=1765010726\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018340/extras/cfb4d220ad36066eb655a6d64bb5bfd4.poster.avif?t=1765010726\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018340/extras/cfb4d220ad36066eb655a6d64bb5bfd4.webm?t=1765010726\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018340/extras/cfb4d220ad36066eb655a6d64bb5bfd4.mp4?t=1765010726\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Have fun, alone or with friends!</strong></p>",
